<p class="header noPspace" dir="ltr">Adoptive and Foster Moms Group</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">Tuesdays: January 28-May 27</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">9:30-11:30am at Crossroads Florence</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">This Bible-based study is designed to help adoptive and foster moms better understand how to build strong and lasting connections with their children as they seek to love and care for them in a way that honors God. The study is based on Dr. Karyn Purvis&rsquo;s book,&nbsp;<a href="http://mandrillapp.com/track/click.php?u=30027655&amp;id=621d241e9ed54a8499fb0639f82bff53&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fempoweredtoconnect.org%2Fbook%2F&amp;url_id=d2acc6c69eea7223eb80604137668a4a3baa9165">The Connected Child.</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><a href="http://www.crossroads.net/my/signup/2003201">Click here to sign up for the upcoming Florence Moms group</a></p>
